---
import NewLayout from '../../layouts/NewLayout.astro'
---

<NewLayout
  title="お問い合わせ | ECモンスター"
  description="ECモンスターへのお問い合わせ。ご質問・ご相談はこちらからお気軽にどうぞ。">

<style>
.ct-hero{background:#111;padding:120px 60px 80px;text-align:center}
.ct-hero-ey{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--red);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.15em;margin-bottom:20px}
.ct-hero h1{font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,44px);font-weight:900;color:#fff;line-height:1.35}

.ct-body{max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 60px}
.ct-lead{font-size:15px;color:var(--light);line-height:2;text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px}

.ct-form{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px}
.ct-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px}
.ct-field input,.ct-field textarea{width:100%;padding:14px 16px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r);font-size:15px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--dark);background:var(--white);transition:.2s;outline:none}
.ct-field input:focus,.ct-field textarea:focus{border-color:var(--dark)}
.ct-field textarea{resize:vertical;min-height:140px;line-height:1.8}
.ct-field input::placeholder,.ct-field textarea::placeholder{color:var(--muted)}
.ct-submit{background:var(--dark);color:var(--white);border:none;padding:16px 40px;border-radius:var(--r);font-size:15px;font-weight:700;font-family:inherit;cursor:pointer;transition:.3s;width:100%}
.ct-submit:hover{background:var(--red)}
.ct-submit:disabled{opacity:.6;cursor:not-allowed}

.ct-alt{background:var(--off);padding:64px 60px;text-align:center;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.ct-alt h2{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:12px}
.ct-alt p{font-size:14px;color:var(--light);margin-bottom:24px}
.ct-alt a{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:var(--dark);color:var(--white);padding:14px 32px;border-radius:var(--r);font-size:14px;font-weight:600;transition:.3s}
.ct-alt a:hover{background:var(--red)}

@media(max-width:768px){
  .ct-hero{padding:100px 24px 60px}
  .ct-body{padding:48px 24px}
  .ct-row{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .ct-alt{padding:48px 24px}
}
</style>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="ct-hero">
  <div class="ct-hero-ey fade">Contact</div>
  <h1 class="fade">お問い合わせ</h1>
</section>

<!-- FORM -->
<section class="ct-body">
  <p class="ct-lead fade">ご質問等ございましたらお気軽にお問い合わせください。<br>お問い合わせは、当社営業時間に順次対応させていただきます。<br>内容によっては返信に時間を要する場合がございます。</p>

  <form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" id="contact-form" class="ct-form fade">
    <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="ed53efba-9f1e-4bf3-aa00-7d68b21d8464" />
    <input type="hidden" name="redirect" value="/contact/thanks/" />
    <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="ecmonster.jp お問い合わせ" />
    <input type="checkbox" name="botcheck" style="display:none" />

    <div class="ct-row">
      <div class="ct-field">
        <input type="text" name="your-name" placeholder="名前*" required autocomplete="name" maxlength="400" />
      </div>
      <div class="ct-field">
        <input type="email" name="your-email" placeholder="メール*" required autocomplete="email" maxlength="400" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ct-field">
      <input type="tel" name="your-tel" placeholder="電話番号" autocomplete="tel" maxlength="400" />
    </div>
    <div class="ct-field">
      <textarea name="your-message" placeholder="コメント*" required maxlength="2000"></textarea>
    </div>
    <div class="ct-field">
      <button type="submit" class="ct-submit" id="submit-btn">送信する</button>
    </div>
  </form>

  <script is:inline>
  document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
    var btn = document.getElementById('submit-btn');
    if (btn.disabled) { e.preventDefault(); return; }
    btn.disabled = true;
    btn.textContent = '送信中...';
    setTimeout(function() { btn.disabled = false; btn.textContent = '送信する'; }, 5000);
  });
  </script>
</section>

<!-- ALT CTA -->
<section class="ct-alt">
  <h2>個別面談で直接ご相談もできます</h2>
  <p>オンラインで30〜60分、御社の状況に合わせてご提案します。</p>
  <a href="https://learn.ecmonster.jp/b/page/3/" target="_blank">個別面談を予約する →</a>
</section>

</NewLayout>
